---
layout: layouts/default
title: Books
metaTagline: A list of books that I'm currently reading or finished reading, to the best of my memory.
---

<p class="mb-4">
  {{ metaTagline }} Read about how I created this page in
  <a href="/posts/2025/creating-a-books-page">this blog post</a>.
</p>

<p class="mb-4">Last updated: {{ books.lastUpdated | dateByFormat("MMMM d, y") }}</p>

<div>
  Jump to:
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#current">Currently Reading</a></li>
    <li><a href="#finished">Finished Reading</a></li>
    <li><a href="#wtr">Want to Read</a></li>
    <li><a href="#dnf">Did Not Finish</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="mt-8">
  <h2 class="my-4 text-lg font-bold" id="current">Currently Reading</h2>
  <div class="grid gap-6 [grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(144px,1fr))]">
    {%- for book in books.current %}
      <div class="w-32 text-sm">
        <a href="{{ book.goodreadsLink }}"
          ><img
            class="w-100 mb-2 hover:rounded hover:outline hover:outline-4 hover:outline-blue-600"
            src="https://placehold.co/120x180?text={{ book.title[0] }}"
        /></a>
        <a class="font-bold" href="{{ book.goodreadsLink }}">{{ book.title }}</a>
        <p>{{ book.author }}</p>
      </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-8">
  <h2 class="my-4 text-lg font-bold" id="finished">Finished Reading ({{ books.read.length }})</h2>
  <div class="grid gap-6 [grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(144px,1fr))]">
    {%- for book in books.read %}
      <div class="w-32 text-sm">
        <a href="{{ book.goodreadsLink }}"
          ><img
            class="w-100 mb-2 hover:rounded hover:outline hover:outline-4 hover:outline-blue-600"
            src="https://placehold.co/120x180?text={{ book.title[0] }}"
        /></a>
        <a class="font-bold" href="{{ book.goodreadsLink }}">{{ book.title }}</a>
        <p>{{ book.author }}</p>
        <p>{{ book.dateRead | dateByFormat("MMM yyyy") }}</p>
      </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-8">
  <h2 class="my-4 text-lg font-bold" id="wtr">Want to Read</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">I'll definitely get around to reading those ADHD books one day...</p>
  <details>
    <summary>List of books</summary>
    <ul>
      {%- for book in books.wtr %}
        <li class="my-2">
          <a class="font-bold" href="{{ book.goodreadsLink }}">{{ book.title }}</a>
          {{ book.author }}
        </li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>
  </details>
</div>

<div class="mt-8">
  <h2 class="my-4 text-lg font-bold" id="dnf">Did Not Finish</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">
    While there's usually no specific reason why I choose not to finish a book, generally it comes down to "just
    couldn't get into it".
  </p>
  <details>
    <summary>List of books</summary>
    <ul>
      {%- for book in books.dnf %}
        <li class="my-2">
          <a class="font-bold" href="{{ book.goodreadsLink }}">{{ book.title }}</a>
          {{ book.author }}
        </li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>
  </details>
</div>
